subject: Software bug report
body: I found a bug in your mobile app. When I try to upload a photo, the app crashes. This happens every time on my iPhone 12.

subject: Partnership opportunity
body: I'm reaching out from TechCorp to discuss a potential partnership. We think there's great synergy between our products and would love to explore collaboration opportunities.

subject: Billing dispute
body: I was charged twice for the same service this month. I've already paid once and don't understand why I'm being charged again. Please fix this immediately.

subject: Feature request
body: It would be great if you could add a calendar integration feature. Many of your competitors have this and it would make your platform much more useful for our team.

subject: API documentation request
body: Do you have API documentation available? I'm a developer and would like to integrate your service with our internal tools.

subject: Login problems
body: I can't log into my account. The system keeps saying my email doesn't exist, but I've been using this account for months.

subject: Custom solution inquiry
body: We have a unique use case that requires custom development. Can you provide a quote for building a specialized version of your platform?

subject: Service outage complaint
body: Your service was down for 3 hours yesterday during our busiest time. This cost us thousands in lost revenue. We need compensation.

subject: Positive feedback
body: I've been using your service for 6 months now and I'm extremely satisfied. The customer support is responsive and the product quality is excellent.

subject: Data export question
body: Is it possible to export my data in different formats? I need CSV and JSON exports for my reporting system.

subject: Mobile app issues
body: The mobile app is very slow on my Android device. It takes 10-15 seconds to load any page. This makes it unusable for me.

subject: Enterprise demo request
body: We're evaluating enterprise solutions and would like to see a demo of your platform. Can someone from your sales team schedule a call?

subject: Refund request
body: I cancelled my subscription 2 weeks ago but you're still charging me. I want a refund for the unauthorized charges.

subject: Usability feedback
body: The new interface is much better than the old one. The navigation is intuitive and the search function works perfectly now.

subject: Integration questions
body: What third-party services do you integrate with? I'm specifically looking for Slack and Trello integration.
